text:
Good work.
I hope we'll have another chance to work together.

Thank you very much!
I'll definitely make it out to your live, Fuyuko-chan.

Wah, that makes me happy...!
Please follow after Fuyu!

As expected, Fuyuko.
Even the staff have completely become your fans.

Like I said, that much is obvious.
These are great opportunities for people to discover Fuyu.

Anytime that I'm in front of everyone,
I've got to be a perfect "Fuyu".
...By the way, do you have time after this?

I'd like to check out some shops,
but I'm a little concerned about how well know Straylight is now.

Sure, I don't mind.
For something like that I'll come with you.
